            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">史密斯档案馆/阿拉米</span></div></div></div><p>这位作曲家根据革命性的思想创作了尖锐、困难的音乐。欣赏它的力量需要练习。<em>蒂姆·佩奇的评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/schoenberg-review-hard-to-like-impossible-to-ignore-99e96580?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
